  "original_title": "\u0b85\u0ba9\u0bc8\u0bb5\u0bb0\u0bc1\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bc1\u0bae\u0bcd \u0ba8\u0bbf\u0bb5\u0bbe\u0bb0\u0ba3\u0bae\u0bcd: \u0b9a\u0b9c\u0bbf\u0ba4\u0bcd \u0b95\u0bcb\u0bb0\u0bbf\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bc8",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Relief for all: Sajid demands",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Leader of Opposition Sajith Premadasa said that 220 lakh people of this country have been subjected to political revenge and the government should take action to save them from revenge.",
        "The leader of the opposition party said that it is reported that the budding party is rapidly involved in the process of presenting a cabinet document through the Prime Minister's Office regarding the compensation of a group of government officials who have suffered political revenge, and he said that he will never allow such an action to be taken at this time.",
        "The Leader of the Opposition said the above while attending a meeting held yesterday (17) at the Office of the Leader of the Opposition in Colombo.",
        "The leader of the opposition said that due to arbitrary decision banning of fertilizers has damaged the crops of the farmers and even today they have not been paid compensation. He also said that the children of this country have not received proper education for more than two years.",
        "He also expressed his opposition to giving favors to selected few under the guise of such political vendettas, abandoning the development of the troubled country. (a)"
      ],
